---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="SEO Services | Shelby Web Company"
  description="Professional SEO services in Shelby, NC. Complete search engine optimization including technical SEO, on-page optimization, local search dominance, and Google Business Profile management."
>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 px-4" data-animate>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-brand-glow text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">✦ Search Engine Optimization</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight whitespace-nowrap">
        Complete <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue via-brand-blueLight to-brand-sky">SEO Services</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
        Comprehensive search engine optimization services that cover every aspect of SEO. From technical optimization to content strategy, we help local businesses dominate search results.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contact#get-in-touch"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-brand-accentLight shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(132,204,22,0.3)] transition-all duration-300"
      >
        Get Your Free SEO Audit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-brand-dark" data-animate>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-brand-glow text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">✦ What We Offer</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Comprehensive SEO Solutions
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Technical SEO</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Site speed optimization, mobile responsiveness, and technical improvements that boost your search rankings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">On-Page Optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Keyword research, meta tags, content optimization, and internal linking to improve your page rankings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Local Search Dominance</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Optimize for local search to appear in Google Maps and local pack results for your service area.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Google Business Profile</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Setup, optimization, and management of your Google Business Profile for maximum local visibility.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Performance Tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Regular reports on rankings, traffic, and conversions so you can see the ROI of your SEO investment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-darkest border border-brand-sky/40 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,200,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-sky to-brand-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width={2} d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Competitor Analysis</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm">Analyze your competitors' strategies and find opportunities to outrank them in search results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 relative overflow-hidden" data-animate>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-darkest via-brand-dark to-brand-darkest"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-sky/10 to-brand-cyan/10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Boost Your Rankings?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
        Let's optimize your website for search success. Get in touch today for a free SEO audit.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contact#get-in-touch"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-brand-accentLight shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(132,204,22,0.3)] transition-all duration-300"
      >
        Get Started Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
